  <h1 class="faqq">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
  <p class="fapp">
      Got a question? We're here to answer! If you don't see<br> 
      your question here, drop us a line on our Feedback page.
  </p>
  
  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <div class="container mt-5">
      <div class="faq-container">
      <!-- FAQ 1 -->
<div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(1)">
        <span>What is the Daily Intake Tracker?</span>
        <span class="close-btn" onclick="closeAnswer(event, 1)">×</span>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-answer" id="answer1">
        The Daily Intake Tracker helps users log their daily meals, fluids, snacks, fruits, and junk food to maintain healthy eating habits and track progress over time.
    </div>
</div>

<!-- FAQ 2 -->
<div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(2)">
        <span>Can I view and download my previous intake reports?</span>
        <span class="close-btn" onclick="closeAnswer(event, 2)">×</span>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-answer" id="answer2">
        Yes, FitHealth stores all your daily intake reports, which can be viewed in tabular form and downloaded as PDFs for personal reference.
    </div>
</div>

<!-- FAQ 3 -->
<div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(3)">
        <span>How does the BMI calculator work?</span>
        <span class="close-btn" onclick="closeAnswer(event, 3)">×</span>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-answer" id="answer3">
        The BMI calculator uses your height and weight to determine your Body Mass Index and categorize you as underweight, normal, overweight, or obese.
    </div>
</div>

<!-- FAQ 4 -->
<div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(4)">
        <span>What types of eye tests are available?</span>
        <span class="close-btn" onclick="closeAnswer(event, 4)">×</span>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-answer" id="answer4">
        FitHealth offers three online eye tests to evaluate your vision accuracy, focus speed, and cognitive flexibility based on standard medical formats.
    </div>
</div>

<!-- FAQ 5 -->
<div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(5)">
        <span>Is my personal health data secure on this platform?</span>
        <span class="close-btn" onclick="closeAnswer(event, 5)">×</span>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-answer" id="answer5">
        Yes, we prioritize data privacy and ensure that all user data is securely stored and used only to enhance your health insights and reports.
    </div>
</div>

<!-- FAQ 6 -->
<div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(6)">
        <span>What health risks does FitHealth help identify?</span>
        <span class="close-btn" onclick="closeAnswer(event, 6)">×</span>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-answer" id="answer6">
        Based on your inputs and test results, FitHealth can give early insights into potential risks like obesity, high BMI, eye strain, and unhealthy eating patterns.
    </div>
</div>

<!-- FAQ 7 -->
<div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(7)">
        <span>Does the site give personalized health suggestions?</span>
        <span class="close-btn" onclick="closeAnswer(event, 7)">×</span>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-answer" id="answer7">
        Yes! Your results from the intake tracker, BMI, and eye tests are used to provide personalized feedback and healthy living tips.
    </div>
</div>

<!-- FAQ 8 -->
<div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(8)">
        <span>Is the platform suitable for all users?</span>
        <span class="close-btn" onclick="closeAnswer(event, 8)">×</span>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-answer" id="answer8">
        FitHealth is designed for users of all ages, but younger users are advised to explore the platform with parental guidance for best understanding.
    </div>
</div>

<!-- FAQ 9 -->
<div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(9)">
        <span>Can I switch between dark and light mode?</span>
        <span class="close-btn" onclick="closeAnswer(event, 9)">×</span>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-answer" id="answer9">
        Yes, FitHealth supports dark/light mode toggling to reduce eye strain and provide a comfortable viewing experience based on your preference.
    </div>
</div>

<!-- FAQ 10 -->
<div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(10)">
        <span>How can I give feedback or ask for help?</span>
        <span class="close-btn" onclick="closeAnswer(event, 10)">×</span>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-answer" id="answer10">
        You can submit your feedback, ask questions, or report any issues using the Feedback page available in the navigation menu.
    </div>
</div>

<!-- FAQ 11 -->
<div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(11)">
        <span>How often should I update my intake and health data?</span>
        <span class="close-btn" onclick="closeAnswer(event, 11)">×</span>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-answer" id="answer11">
        For accurate insights, we recommend logging your data daily or whenever your diet, habits, or routine changes significantly.
    </div>
</div>

<!-- FAQ 12 -->
<div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(12)">
        <span>Can I track improvements over time?</span>
        <span class="close-btn" onclick="closeAnswer(event, 12)">×</span>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-answer" id="answer12">
        Yes, all past intake logs and test results are saved so you can monitor your health trends and improvements month-to-month.
    </div>
</div>

